'''TrackInsight''' is a free [[exchange-traded funds]] analysis platform founded in 2014 by Jean-René Giraud and Arnaud Izard.<ref>{{cite web|title=Company Overview of TrackInsight SAS|url=https://www.bloomberg.com/research/stocks/private/snapshot.asp?privcapId=405206468|website=Bloomberg|accessdate=2017-12-06}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=TrackInsight|url=https://www.crunchbase.com/organization/trackinsight|website=Crunchbase|accessdate=2018-03-12}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://bourse.lefigaro.fr/fonds-trackers/actu-conseils/koris-international-lance-trackinsight-plateforme-d-analyse-de-la-qualite-de-replication-des-2712986|title=Koris International lance TrackInsight, plateforme d'analyse de la qualité de réplication des principaux ETFs Européens|last=|first=|date=2014-10-20|work=|access-date=2018-03-09|archive-url=|archive-date=|dead-url=|website=Le Figaro|language=fr}}</ref>

The service provides ratings<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.etf.com/sections/features-and-news/10889-trackinsight-launches-etf-ratings-service|title=TrackInsight Launches ETF Ratings Service|last=Rachael Revesz|first=|date=2015-06-05|work=|access-date=2018-03-09|archive-url=|archive-date=|dead-url=|website=ETF.com|language=en}}</ref> and comparison tools on [[exchange-traded funds]] distributed in [[North America]], [[Europe]] and [[Asia]].

On October 17, 2016, TrackInsight raised €2,500,000 from [[NewAlpha Asset Management]] and [[Aviva|Aviva Group]].<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.investmenteurope.net/regions/france/etf-platform-trackinsight-raises-e2-5m-from-new-alpha-and-aviva-france/|title=ETF platform TrackInsight raises €2.5m from New Alpha and Aviva France|last=Jonathan Boyd|first=|date=2016-10-17|work=|access-date=2017-12-06|archive-url=|archive-date=|dead-url=|website=InvestmentEurope|language=en}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.boursorama.com/actualites/trackinsight-leve-2-5-millions-d-euros-aupres-de-newalpha-et-aviva-france-17537b1c3b14fa6b550fc7f09eefc473|title=Trackinsight lève 2,5 millions d'euros auprès de NewAlpha et Aviva France|last=|first=|date=2016-10-20|work=|access-date=2017-12-06|archive-url=|archive-date=|dead-url=|website=Boursorama|language=fr}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://bourse.lefigaro.fr/fonds-trackers/actu-conseils/new-alpha-am-et-aviva-investissent-2-5-millions-d-euros-dans-trackinsight-5865387|title=New Alpha AM et Aviva investissent 2,5 millions d'euros dans TrackInsight|last=|first=|date=2016-10-17|work=|access-date=2018-03-09|archive-url=|archive-date=|dead-url=|website=Le Figaro|language=fr}}</ref>

